public class TableField
extends cds.savot.model.SavotField

The TableField class is used to represent a field of a table (or a field of a data model stored in a table).

newSavotField

public cds.savot.model.SavotField newSavotField(java.lang.String ns)
Contruct a SavotField instance with the correct name space set for the UTYPE tag. The UTYPE name space prefix is used only in XML contexts such as VOTable.

Parameters:
ns - XML namespace prefix to be used.
